RapidSMS app for using USSD services on GSM networks:
    - check SIM balance
    - transfer airtime

NOTE: this app is not for the feint of heart in its present condition
    - not yet updated to work with latest RapidSMS code
    - only works with a custom version of pygsm: http://github.com/ewheeler/pygsm
    - requires customization depending on mobile network
